  "bodyHtml": "<span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">As part of your onboarding, Back Market requests sellers to provide their company identification in the &quot;Company Identification Number&quot; section under the Legal Details tab in their Back Office. This identification number is the ID issued by the companies, trade or commerce registry (or equivalent) in your country. It may vary depending on your country, so please refer to the table below to determine which number to provide.</span><br><br> \n<table border=\"1\" style=\"width: 1200px;height: 1500px;\"><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>Country</strong></span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>Identifier name</strong></span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>Short name</strong></span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>Useful Links</strong></span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>Austria</strong></span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Firmenbuchnummer</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">FB-Nr.</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Issued by the Austrian business register:<br>\t\t\t<strong>https://www.usp.gv.at/Portal.Node/usp/public/content/laufender_betrieb/firmenbuch/firmenbuchabfrage/Seite.760006.html</strong></span></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>Australia</strong></span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Australia Business Number</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">ABN</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">https://www.abr.gov.au/</span></strong></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>Belgium</strong></span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Numéro d&#39;entreprise / Ondernemingsnummer / Unternehmensnummer</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"> </td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"> </td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>China</strong></span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Credibility Code, or USCN code</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"> </td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"> </td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><strong>Chypre</strong></span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\">Αριθμός Εγγραφής στο Τμήμα Εφόρου Εταιρειών και Επίσημου Παραλήπτη</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"text-align: center;\